metadata.name: Welcome to clowns world
metadata.description: The circus is a place where we go to escape the harsh realities of the world and to be transported to a realm of wonder and magic. But behind the brightly colored tents and the laughter of the crowds, there are those who perform who are hiding a deeper sadness. The clowns, with their painted faces and exaggerated expressions, are the embodiment of this dichotomy. They bring joy to others, but their own souls are heavy with sorrow.
